{"tid":121633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 比人扣糧點算","createTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T11:43:02.000Z","uid":78120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcfed1241782d3032708bea64bb9f4268e4ce821","tid":121633,"uid":78120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"我番兼職老麥<br />\n之前新年就講明雙工 番夠9個鐘有百二津貼<br />\n個幾日忙撚到仆街<br />\n不過心諗有雙糧就忍埋佢 <br />\n<br />\n點知早幾日出糧睇番<br />\n少撚左成截錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就問個經理啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂新年個陣唔係計雙糧咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吓你唔知咩係雙工咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔係雙倍人工咩？即係點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：即係冇<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<br />\n個陣講明雙工依加又話冇<br />\n我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 dse雞"},{"pid":"b5b6403e02ff410a50b780a486e0cfd4b76e795c","tid":121633,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:43:02.000Z","msg":"有無白紙黑字寫明雙工<br />\n無就拜拜<br />\n有就勞記見<br />\n可以問下同事有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}